00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:14.470 align:middle line:84%
If you want to learn more ways
to re-balance your hormones

00:09:14.470 --> 00:09:16.540 align:middle line:84%
again, I would love
it if you would

00:09:16.540 --> 00:09:18.920 align:middle line:90%
read my book the "Hormone Cure."

00:09:18.920 --> 00:09:20.740 align:middle line:84%
I've got about 100
more tips to share

00:09:20.740 --> 00:09:23.880 align:middle line:84%
with you that are
evidence-based, fun,

00:09:23.880 --> 00:09:25.320 align:middle line:84%
and really move
the needle when it

00:09:25.320 --> 00:09:27.885 align:middle line:84%
comes to creating
natural hormone balance.

00:09:27.885 --> 00:09:28.934 align:middle line:90%
