00:50:14.350 --> 00:50:16.760 align:middle line:84%
So when women enter
perimenopause,

00:50:16.760 --> 00:50:19.330 align:middle line:84%
I sometimes call it
the perfect storm

00:50:19.330 --> 00:50:22.440 align:middle line:84%
because it tends to be that
