00:50:22.440 --> 00:50:23.430 align:middle line:90%
affected.

00:50:23.430 --> 00:50:26.590 align:middle line:84%
Your estrogen is out of
balance with progesterone,

00:50:26.590 --> 00:50:28.920 align:middle line:84%
your cortisol is either
high or low or both

00:50:28.920 --> 00:50:32.410 align:middle line:84%
within the same day, and
your thyroid is probably off.

00:50:32.410 --> 00:50:34.180 align:middle line:84%
Over the age of 40,
there's this problem

00:50:34.180 --> 00:50:37.690 align:middle line:84%
