00:51:11.590 --> 00:51:13.844 align:middle line:84%
>> LISA: It's not
necessarily thyroid related?

00:51:13.844 --> 00:51:15.260 align:middle line:84%
>> GOTTFRIED: It
could be thyroid,

00:51:15.260 --> 00:51:19.220 align:middle line:84%
but the important point here
is to address the hormones.

00:51:19.220 --> 00:51:21.830 align:middle line:84%
I think a lot of women
start making lists.

00:51:21.830 --> 00:51:24.370 align:middle line:84%
They start to get obsessive
about writing things down

00:51:24.370 --> 00:51:26.560 align:middle line:84%
