00:51:28.370 --> 00:51:31.210 align:middle line:84%
to say this is
probably perimenopause.

00:51:31.210 --> 00:51:33.410 align:middle line:84%
You want to get your
hormones into balance.

00:51:33.410 --> 00:51:36.990 align:middle line:84%
Don't reach for the
latest ADD medication

00:51:36.990 --> 00:51:40.470 align:middle line:84%
because there's a good chance
that the problem is hormonal.

